==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dipterous
<hw>Dip"ter*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having two wings, as certain insects; belonging
to the order Diptera.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having two wings;
two-winged.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dipterygian</ent>⟦br⟧
